rvice platform that helps you balance everything your customers need to be happy.","about.features.feature2.descriptionAr":"منصة خدمة عملاء شاملة تساعدك على موازنة كل ما يحتاجه عملاؤك ليكونوا سعداء.","about.features.feature3.titleEn":"Manage your team with reports","about.features.feature3.titleAr":"إدارة فريقك بالتقارير","about.features.feature3.descriptionEn":"Measure what matters with Untitled's easy-to-use reports. You can filter, export, and drilldown on the data in a couple clicks.","about.features.feature3.descriptionAr":"قس ما يهم بتقارير سهلة الاستخدام. يمكنك التصفية والتصدير والتعمق في البيانات بنقرات قليلة.","about.team.headingEn":"Meet our team","about.team.headingAr":"قابل فريقنا","about.team.subheadingEn":"Our philosophy is simple—hire a team of diverse, passionate people and foster a culture that empowers you to do your best work.","about.team.subheadingAr":"فلسفتنا بسيطة - توظيف فريق متنوع من الأشخاص المتحمسين وتعزيز ثقافة تمكنك من القيام بأفضل عمل لك.","about.team.viewAllEn":"View all creators","about.team.viewAllAr":"عرض جميع المبدعين","servicesPage.badgeEn":"Services","servicesPage.titleEn":"What we offer","servicesPage.descriptionEn":"Comprehensive digital solutions for your business.","servicesPage.descriptionAr":"حلول رقمية شاملة لأعمالك.","servicesPage.filters.viewAllEn":"View all","servicesPage.filters.designEn":"Design","servicesPage.filters.designAr":"التصميم","servicesPage.filters.marketingEn":"Marketing","servicesPage.filters.marketingAr":"التسويق","servicesPage.filters.softwareEn":"Software","servicesPage.filters.softwareAr":"البرمجيات","serviceCard.requestPricingEn":"Request pricing","serviceCard.viewWorkSamplesEn":"View work samples","serviceCard.viewWorkSamplesAr":"عرض عينات العمل","work.titleEn":"Our Work","work.titleAr":"أعمالنا","work.subtitleEn":"Explore our projects","work.subtitleAr":"استكشف مشاريعنا","workCard.seeFullProjectEn":"See full project","workCard.seeFullProjectAr":"عرض المشروع كاملاً","workCard.seeLiveChannelsEn":"See