084/Gemini_Generated_Image_pw5ia5pw5ia5pw5i_1_mw5kwl.png","about.features.feature3.item1En":"Filter, export, and drilldown on the data quickly","about.features.feature3.item1Ar":"التصفية والتصدير والتعمق في البيانات بسرعة","about.features.feature3.item2En":"Save, schedule, and automate reports to your inbox","about.features.feature3.item2Ar":"احفظ وجدول وأتمت التقارير إلى بريدك الوارد","about.features.feature3.item3En":"Connect the tools you already use with 100+ integrations","about.features.feature3.item3Ar":"ربط الأدوات التي تستخدمها بالفعل مع أكثر من 100 تكامل","about.features.feature3.imageUrl":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dlbkla9nz/image/upload/v1773027093/Gemini_Generated_Image_pw5ia5pw5ia5pw5i_2_yb932t.png","about.team.hideViewAll":"false","footer.socialLinks":"[{name:facebook, href:https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61556612142969, icon:facebook}]"},"children":"$L1e"}]}]]}]
